-- Mizuho to Arrange China Development's $400 Million Bond Sale, Nikkei Says
-- Fergus Maguire
-- 2010-07-04T21:13:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-04/mizuho-to-arrange-china-development-s-400-million-bond-sale-nikkei-says.html

          
          
             Mizuho Corporate Bank will arrange a
$400 million bond sale by China Development Bank Corp. this
month, the first foreign bank to act as the principal
underwriter for a bond issuance by a Chinese bank, Nikkei
English News said, without citing anyone.  
          
          


  


        